---
const title = 'Privacy Policy — Peek';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content="Peek Privacy Policy — data protection statement in accordance with GDPR." />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #0b1020;
        --panel: rgba(16, 24, 48, 0.8);
        --text: #eef2ff;
        --muted: #a6b0cf;
        --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        --accent: #7c9cff;
        --accent-2: #67e8f9;
        --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(124,156,255,0.18), transparent 25%), radial-gradient(circle at right, rgba(103,232,249,0.12), transparent 20%), var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        min-height: 100vh;
      }
      a { color: var(--accent); }
      .container { width: min(800px, calc(100% - 32px)); margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 0 80px; }
      .brand { font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.02em; font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 40px; display: block; }
      .brand span { color: var(--accent-2); }
      h1 { font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 0 32px; }
      h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--accent-2); margin: 36px 0 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; font-weight: 700; }
      p, li { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; margin: 8px 0; }
      ul { padding-left: 20px; }
      .card { background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 20px; padding: 28px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .meta { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 48px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding-top: 24px; }
      .lang-toggle { margin-bottom: 32px; display: flex; gap: 8px; }
      .lang-btn { padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; }
      .lang-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: var(--text); }
      .lang-btn.active { background: rgba(124,156,255,0.15); border-color: rgba(124,156,255,0.3); color: var(--accent); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <a class="brand" href="/">Peek<span>.</span></a>

      <div class="lang-toggle">
        <a class="lang-btn" href="/privacy">DE</a>
        <a class="lang-btn active" href="/privacy-en">EN</a>
      </div>

      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

      <h2>1. Controller</h2>
      <div class="card">
        <p><strong>Peek Platform GmbH</strong></p>
        <p>Musterstraße 12<br />10115 Berlin<br />Germany</p>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@peek.example">hello@peek.example</a></p>
      </div>

      <h2>2. Data Collection and Processing</h2>
      <p>
        We collect personal data only when you provide it to us through a contact request, newsletter subscription, or use of our services.
        Processing is carried out on the basis of Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR (contract performance) and Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest).
      </p>
      <p>Data we process includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact details (name, email address, phone number)</li>
        <li>Business data sourced from publicly available information (e.g., Google Maps, OpenStreetMap, public registries)</li>
        <li>Usage data (IP address, browser type, access timestamps)</li>
        <li>Preview data generated as part of our one-page preview services</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Purpose of Processing</h2>
      <p>We process your data for the following purposes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Provision and operation of Peek services</li>
        <li>Creation and delivery of one-page business previews</li>
        <li>Communication for support and service requests</li>
        <li>Improvement of our services and user experience</li>
        <li>Compliance with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We do not share your data with third parties without your explicit consent, unless required for the provision of our services
        (e.g., hosting providers) or required by law. All processors are contractually bound to process your data only on our instructions.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Personal data is retained only as long as necessary for the provision of our services or as required by legal retention obligations.
        Business correspondence is retained for a minimum of 3 years.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the following rights with respect to us:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Right of access to your data stored with us (Art. 15 GDPR)</li>
        <li>Right to rectification of inaccurate data (Art. 16 GDPR)</li>
        <li>Right to erasure, where no legal retention obligations conflict (Art. 17 GDPR)</li>
        <li>Right to restriction of processing (Art. 18 GDPR)</li>
        <li>Right to data portability (Art. 20 GDPR)</li>
        <li>Right to object to processing (Art. 21 GDPR)</li>
        <li>Right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority (Art. 77 GDPR)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise your rights, contact: <a href="mailto:hello@peek.example">hello@peek.example</a></p>

      <h2>7. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p>
        Our website uses only technically necessary cookies required for the operation of the site (e.g., session cookies).
        No marketing or tracking cookies are set without your explicit consent.
        You can change your cookie preferences at any time via the banner at the bottom of the page.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Security</h2>
      <p>
        We implement technical and organisational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.
        These include TLS encryption, regular security updates, and access controls.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy as needed, particularly when our services change or legal requirements evolve.
        The current version is always available on this page.
      </p>

      <div class="meta">
        <p>Last updated: April 2025</p>
        <p><a href="/">← Back to homepage</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="/impressum">Impressum</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>